targets.query: from(bucket: "${bucket}")  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)  |> filter(fn: (r) =>     r._measurement == "storage" and    r._field == "diskSpaceTotal")  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: last, createEmpty: false)  |> yield(name: "last")

from(bucket: "${bucket}")  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)  |> filter(fn: (r) =>    r._measurement == "storage" and    r._field == "diskSpaceFree")  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: last, createEmpty: false)  |> yield(name: "last")

from(bucket: "${bucket}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "highResStorage")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "netRecvBytes" or r["_field"] == "netSendBytes" or r["_field"] == "nodeID")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: last, createEmpty: false)
  |> pivot(rowKey: ["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> drop(fn: (column) => column =~ /^_(start|stop)/)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with Throughput: r.netSendBytes + r.netRecvBytes}))
  |> drop(columns: ["netRecvBytes","netSendBytes"])

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    
|> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    
|> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "storageClientOpsByUser" and    r._field == "B-wr")    
|> sum()    |> group()     
|> pivot(rowKey:["user"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")

from(bucket: "${bucket}")  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)  |> filter(fn: (r) =>  r._measurement == "highResStorage" and    r._field == "netRecvBytes")  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: max, createEmpty: false)  |> yield(name: "max")

from(bucket: "${bucket}")  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)  |> filter(fn: (r) =>  r._measurement == "highResStorage" and    r._field == "netSendBytes")  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: max, createEmpty: false)  |> yield(name: "max")

from(bucket: "${bucket}")  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "highResStorage" and    r._field == "diskReadBytes")  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: max, createEmpty: false)  |> yield(name: "max")

from(bucket: "${bucket}")  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)  |> filter(fn: (r) =>    r._measurement == "highResStorage" and    r._field == "diskWriteBytes")  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: max, createEmpty: false)  |> yield(name: "max")

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "meta" and r._field == "isResponding")    |> group(columns: ["nodeID"])    |> last()    |> group()    |> keep(columns: ["nodeID", "_value"])

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "storage" and r._field == "diskSpaceTotal")    |> group(columns: ["nodeID"])    |> last()    |> group()    |> keep(columns: ["_value", "nodeID"])    |> rename(columns: {_value: "Total Space"})

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "storage" and r._field == "diskSpaceFree")    |> group(columns: ["nodeID"])    |> last()    |> group()    |> keep(columns: ["_value", "nodeID"])    |> rename(columns: {_value: "Free Space"})

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "storage" and r._field == "isResponding")    |> group(columns: ["nodeID"])    |> last()    |> group()    |> keep(columns: ["_value", "nodeID"])    |> rename(columns: {_value: "Service Status"})

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    |> filter(fn: (r) => r.nodeID == "${storageID}" and r._measurement == "storageTargets" and r._field == "diskSpaceTotal")    |> group(columns: ["storageTargetID"])    |> last()    |> group()    |> keep(columns: ["_value", "storageTargetID"])    |> rename(columns: {_value: "Total Space"})

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    |> filter(fn: (r) => r.nodeID == "${storageID}" and r._measurement == "storageTargets" and r._field == "diskSpaceFree")    |> group(columns: ["storageTargetID"])    |> last()    |> group()    |> keep(columns: ["_value", "storageTargetID"])    |> rename(columns: {_value: "Free Space"})

from(bucket: "${bucket}")    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)    |> filter(fn: (r) => r.nodeID == "${storageID}" and r._measurement == "storageTargets" and r._field == "targetConsistencyState")    |> group(columns: ["storageTargetID"])    |> last()    |> group()    |> keep(columns: ["_value", "storageTargetID"])    |> rename(columns: {_value: "State"})
